---
import astroLogo from '../assets/astro.svg';
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
---

<div class="hero-container">
	<div class="hero-content">
		<h1 class="title">OpenCRM</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">La solución definitiva de CRM de código abierto</p>
		
		<div class="features-grid">
			<div class="feature-card">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
				</svg>
				<h3>Gestión de Clientes</h3>
				<p>Centraliza toda la información de tus clientes en un solo lugar</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="feature-card">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
				</svg>
				<h3>Análisis Avanzado</h3>
				<p>Toma decisiones basadas en datos con nuestras herramientas analíticas</p>
			</div>

			<div class="feature-card">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="feature-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
				</svg>
				<h3>Automatización</h3>
				<p>Automatiza tareas repetitivas y mejora la productividad</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="cta-buttons">
			<a href="/demo" class="cta-primary">Prueba Gratuita</a>
			<a href="/docs" class="cta-secondary">Documentación</a>
		</div>

		<div class="open-source-badge">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="badge-icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
			</svg>
			<span>100% Open Source</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<style>
	.hero-container {
		min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
		color: #1e293b;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.hero-content {
		max-width: 1200px;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.subtitle {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: #475569;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.features-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.feature-card {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.feature-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.feature-icon {
		width: 3rem;
		height: 3rem;
		color: #0ea5e9;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		display: block;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.feature-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: #1e293b;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.feature-card p {
		color: #64748b;
		font-size: 1rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.cta-primary, .cta-secondary {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 0.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: transform 0.3s ease;
	}

	.cta-primary {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
		color: white;
	}

	.cta-secondary {
		background: white;
		color: #0ea5e9;
		border: 2px solid #0ea5e9;
	}

	.cta-primary:hover, .cta-secondary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.open-source-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
		background: white;
		border-radius: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	.badge-icon {
		width: 1.25rem;
		height: 1.25rem;
		color: #0ea5e9;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.subtitle {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}

		.features-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
		}
	}
</style>
